songs.title: Put In Work (Original)*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

Put in work (Put in work)
Now put in work, put in work (Put in work)
Lil' mama put in work, (yeah) catch these ones, take off your shirt
Bend it over, twerk twerk
I know your body isn't yours, you should get your ass insured
Show me what you worth, baby put in work
